name: Bag spider Scout
description: This Scout has spent his life around local civilisations and adapted unusual camouflage techniques.

name: Carbon Fibre Scout
description: A prototype Scout exoskeleton design produced by the Tarantula spider clan, the light weight design allowed for greater mobility at the cost of survivability on the battlefield.
store_tags: spider; skin; carbon fibre; tarantula; scout;

name: Couch Spider Scout
description: A Tarantula Scout that has been adapted to living within rural enviroments, often found within living quarters of humans.

name: Crack Scout
description: Cracked and weathered, the skin of this Scout is scarred from long journeys across the desert planes.

name: Dirty Scout
description: Long expeditions have dirtied and weathered this Scout so extensively, it is barely recognizable.

name: Frog Scout
description: This rain forest Scout has a mimic technique which allows it to camouflage as a frog to close the distance between them and their prey before striking.

name: Gold Scout
description: Gold taken from ancient ruins and forged into an exoskeleton for this Scout, what this skin lacks in mobility and strength is countered by its ability to harness crystal energy to boast its damage. -

name: Inside out Scout
description: A freak accident within the teleportation process re-materialized this Scout with its exoskeleton inside out, just surviving this accident is a miracle on its own.
store_tags: spider; skin; inside out; tarantula; scout;

name: Iron Scout
description: A brave and sturdy Scout who inhabits industrial zones, they blend into their metal surroundings surviving the most polluted areas.

name: Jade Scout
description: Influenced by the culture of the east, this Scout had covered himself in jade, not only does this allow them to hide among other jade ornaments, but also increases defence measures.

name: Melding Scout
description: As a side effect of living in close proximity to the Great Fire Wurm, this Scout has been covered by a new exotic substance of melted crystal and silicon.

name: Nightmare Scout
description: Experiments, Torture and battle damage, this Scout has survived what most would not want to. Very little remains of what one would call an exoskeleton, exposing the muscle underneath, yet the nightmare continues for those who dare oppose it.

name: Printed Scout
description: 3D Printing brought this Scout to life along with the technologies developed under the Tarantula Spider Kings reigns, it is unknown whether they are mechanical spiders or exoskeleton upgrades.

name: Scally Scout
description: This Scout has covered himself in hardened reptile scales, either scavenged or won through combat. These scales improve survivability, whilst helping with infiltration and camouflage.

name: Swamp Scout
description: The swamp Scout can usually be found in shallow waters and uses vibrations in the water to locate targets around them and patiently wait for their prey to get within striking distance.
